
Epoch 5/30
100000/100000 [==============================] - 695s - loss: 1.7846     
Epoch 6/30
100000/100000 [==============================] - 700s - loss: 1.7418     
Epoch 7/30
100000/100000 [==============================] - 700s - loss: 1.7035     
Epoch 8/30
100000/100000 [==============================] - 698s - loss: 1.6680     
Epoch 9/30
100000/100000 [==============================] - 699s - loss: 1.6341     
Epoch 10/30
100000/100000 [==============================] - 700s - loss: 1.6028     
