
Epoch 11/30
100000/100000 [==============================] - 698s - loss: 1.5718     
Epoch 12/30
100000/100000 [==============================] - 696s - loss: 1.5426     
Epoch 13/30
100000/100000 [==============================] - 695s - loss: 1.5129     
Epoch 14/30
100000/100000 [==============================] - 694s - loss: 1.4836     
Epoch 15/30
100000/100000 [==============================] - 693s - loss: 1.4560     
